MARKSWOMAN broke inwardly, lacked speed along the inside, trailed turning for home, shifted out in upper stretch, ran on willingly outside of rivals in the final furlong and missed reaching show. ZERO CLICK stalked along the inside and faded. WIKI LIO broke outwardly many paths at the start, recovered to track two wide approaching the turn, came under urging in the three path around the bend, shifted out to the five path entering the lane, but tired while hanging on her left lead.
